### Create a new enquiry (Matches SOP)
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "whatsapp",
  "customer_name": "Alice Smith",
  "message": "I would like to know the price of your service."
}

###

### Create a new enquiry (Escalates - no SOP match)
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "email",
  "customer_name": "Bob Jones",
  "message": "I want to talk to a human right now about my account."
}

###

### Schedule a follow-up
# Replace {id} with the ID returned from the creation step
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry/enq_12345678/follow-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 60,
  "message_template": "Just checking in to see if you received our pricing."
}

###

### Escalate an enquiry manually
# Replace {id} with the ID returned from the creation step
POST http://localhost:8000/enquiry/enq_12345678/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer is extremely upset and requested a manager."
}

###

### Get enquiry history
# Replace {id} with the ID returned from the creation step
GET http://localhost:8000/enquiry/enq_12345678/history

###

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
